// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1251 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c638d723-3051-57eb-b28a-4e0d5314cb4a

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
